    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require hospitality businesses provide transport for staff on public holidays",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We want legislation to be passed that makes it mandatory for hospitality employers to provide their workers with transport to and from work, when employees are expected to work on public holidays. There is often no or reduced public transport available, yet staff are often expected to work.",
